fernland
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:country that carries bracken fern or is most likely to revert to fern secondary growth.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: formerly mainly as fern land
